# Trivy false-positive suppressions for this project.
#
# Add entries here when trivy flags a finding that is a known
# false positive for this codebase. Each entry should include:
#   - The Trivy rule ID (e.g., AVD-AZU-0042)
#   - A comment explaining why the suppression is justified
#   - A link to the relevant issue or documentation
#
# Format: one rule ID per line, comments start with #
#
# Example:
# AVD-AZU-0042  # False positive: storage account is internal-only
